@21MegaYoshi Opinion, my friend. Opinion!

Personally, I liked Symphonia a lot. But even if it was one of the best Tales games...it was just a Tales game. The same old orphans, the same old magic trees, the same old clichés.

Many things in Skies of Arcadia sucked. The fighting was uninteresting, for one. ( Note that I am talking about the technically superior Dreamcast version, not the GC one ). But the characters, story, environments and music just made my heart smile. It really did.
